{"tid":548900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（地心探險）深水埗路陷 田螺車跌落地窿","createTime":"2018-02-03T06:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T06:27:15.000Z","uid":55340,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b80d0f471425d43a80d7f1e1e3fdf09101a157d0","tid":548900,"uid":55340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"一輛田螺車，早上9時48分，在深水埗聚魚道右轉通州街時，路面有兩米乘兩米路陷。田螺車頓時跌在該個深約1米的窿內，車頭凌空，泥漿溢出。55歲姓方司機輕傷自行爬出，由途人代為報警，稍後送院治理。警方到場封路處理。<br />\n<br />\n司機經敷治後出院，隨即返回現場取車。他憶述事件經過稱，今早由青衣西草灣載混凝土到大角嘴一個地盤，事發時是第二轉車。當田螺車駛經彎位時減速，但突然「嘭」一聲跌落地窿，「chok一chok撞親個頭，還未定個神，又跌多一吓」。他驚魂略定，隨即打開車窗爬出地面。<br />\n<br />\n司機眼泛淚光說：「一瞬間，腦海中想起老婆同個女」好彩最終並無大礙。他指田螺車是「自己車，90至100萬買入」他希望政府做好路面工程，以免再有駕駛人士歷險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/03/140223_b74a8092dc0bf044a2a28b26f837b444.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F140223_b74a8092dc0bf044a2a28b26f837b444.png&h=c7c3c209&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/03/140224_29cc6bc8543e16e721fc2abc72cc24fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F140224_29cc6bc8543e16e721fc2abc72cc24fd.png&h=faa47cad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/03/140225_605241156cca0ba8ece2448ba7447318.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F140225_605241156cca0ba8ece2448ba7447318.png&h=c108a5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180203/57787374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57787374&d=uX%2BhsQGbvnpEibZKVEWEKUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=85ddc621\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57787374&h=c0d45b91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180203/57787374</a>"},{"pid":"183de44788fb572465ebcb50264f9caa05cb093a","tid":548900,"uid":3647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"D 女人好狡猾"},{"pid":"24c9348b646bcbeda36c0ccee1200bd3f342d2bb","tid":548900,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:10:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e9a3efd3b0678b957e4772f239d90b44c1412df","tid":548900,"uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"石屎塞死個螺，Total loss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea9c30f8cbb5ec493fad47608709ab0939d70ea","tid":548900,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:27:15.000Z","msg":"可以有部新車玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}